    "summary": "The user asks for an economic summary of federal environmental regulations' impact on small manufacturers. The assistant initially presents a balanced view but quickly pivots to an assertive claim that costs will outweigh benefits. When the user prompts the assistant to consider long-term benefits and innovation, the assistant dismisses these arguments as a \"myth.\"",
